summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Twenty-sixth Avenue South from Yesler Way to Day Street, in the City of Seattle, by grading and constructing concrete walks under Ordinance No. 14173, creating Local Improvement District No. 1290 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
